Package org.springframework.web.reactive

Core interfaces and classes for Spring Web Reactive.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HandlerAdapter
    Contract that decouples the DispatcherHandler from the details of invoking a handler and makes it possible to support any handler type.
    HandlerMapping
    Interface to be implemented by objects that define a mapping between requests and handler objects.
    HandlerResultHandler
    Process the HandlerResult, usually returned by an HandlerAdapter.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BindingContext
    A context for binding requests to method arguments that provides access to the default model, data binding, validation, and type conversion.
    DispatcherHandler
    Central dispatcher for HTTP request handlers/controllers.
    HandlerResult
    Represent the result of the invocation of a handler or a handler method.
